import React from 'react';
import {
  Container,
  Typography,
  Box,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  Grid,
  LinearProgress,
  Chip,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  TrendingUp,
  TrendingDown,
  FitnessCenter,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const Progress: React.FC = () => {
  const progressStats = [
    {
      title: 'Weight Progress',
      current: 68.5,
      target: 65,
      unit: 'kg',
      change: -1.5,
      icon: <TrendingDown />,
      color: 'success',
    },
    {
      title: 'BMI',
      current: 22.1,
      target: 21.0,
      unit: '',
      change: -0.4,
      icon: <TrendingDown />,
      color: 'success',
    },
    {
      title: 'Workouts This Month',
      current: 12,
      target: 20,
      unit: 'sessions',
      change: +3,
      icon: <TrendingUp />,
      color: 'primary',
    },
    {
      title: 'Calories Burned',
      current: 8500,
      target: 12000,
      unit: 'kcal',
      change: +2100,
      icon: <TrendingUp />,
      color: 'warning',
    },
  ];

  const weeklyGoals = [
    { goal: 'Exercise 5 times', completed: 3, total: 5 },
    { goal: 'Drink 8 glasses of water daily', completed: 5, total: 7 },
    { goal: 'Get 8 hours of sleep', completed: 4, total: 7 },
    { goal: 'Eat 5 servings of vegetables', completed: 6, total: 7 },
  ];

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg">
      <Box sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        <Typography variant="h4" component="h1" gutterBottom>
          Progress Tracker
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
          Monitor your fitness journey and celebrate your achievements
        </Typography>
      </Box>

      {/* Progress Stats */}
      <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
        {progressStats.map((stat, index) => (
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3} key={index}>
            <Card>
              <CardContent>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                  <Box sx={{ color: `${stat.color}.main`, mr: 1 }}>
                    {stat.icon}
                  </Box>
                  <Typography variant="h6" component="div">
                    {stat.current} {stat.unit}
                  </Typography>
                </Box>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                  {stat.title}
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 1, mb: 1 }}>
                  <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary">
                    Target: {stat.target} {stat.unit}
                  </Typography>
                  <Chip
                    label={`${stat.change > 0 ? '+' : ''}${stat.change} ${stat.unit}`}
                    size="small"
                    color={stat.change > 0 ? 'success' : 'error'}
                  />
                </Box>
                <LinearProgress
                  variant="determinate"
                  value={Math.min((stat.current / stat.target) * 100, 100)}
                  color={stat.color as any}
                />
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        ))}
      </Grid>

      {/* Weekly Goals */}
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                This Week's Goals
              </Typography>
              {weeklyGoals.map((goal, index) => (
                <Box key={index} sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', mb: 1 }}>
                    <Typography variant="body2">{goal.goal}</Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                      {goal.completed}/{goal.total}
                    </Typography>
                  </Box>
                  <LinearProgress
                    variant="determinate"
                    value={(goal.completed / goal.total) * 100}
                    color={goal.completed >= goal.total ? 'success' : 'primary'}
                  />
                </Box>
              ))}
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Recent Achievements
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center', py: 4 }}>
                <FitnessCenter sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: 'primary.main', mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom>
                  First Week Complete! 🎉
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  You completed your first week of workouts
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      {/* Weight Chart Placeholder */}
      <Card sx={{ mt: 3 }}>
        <CardContent>
          <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
            Weight Progress Chart
          </Typography>
          <Box sx={{
            height: 300,
            display: 'flex',
            alignItems: 'center',
            justifyContent: 'center',
            backgroundColor: 'grey.50',
            borderRadius: 1
          }}>
            <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
              Chart visualization coming soon...
            </Typography>
          </Box>
        </CardContent>
      </Card>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default Progress;
